```

### Method Names

```go
// Prefer short verbs
Calc()  not  Calculate()
Exec()  not  Execute()
Init()  not  Initialize()
Proc()  not  Process()
Gen()   not  Generate()

// Getters don't use Get
Price()     not  GetPrice()
