5. [File Management](#file-management)
6. [Code Organization](#code-organization)
7. [Testing Standards](#testing-standards)
8. [Documentation Rules](#documentation-rules)

## Core Philosophy

### The Big Meanie Way

```go
// We value:
// 1. Clarity over cleverness
// 2. Breaking changes over hidden complexity
// 3. Direct solutions over abstractions
// 4. Fast failures over graceful degradation
// 5. Today's correctness over tomorrow's flexibility
```

### Design Principles

```go
// BAD: Maintaining compatibility
type OrderService interface {
    PlaceOrder(order Order) error
    PlaceOrderV2(order OrderV2) error  // NEVER DO THIS
}

// GOOD: Clean break
type OrderService interface {
    PlaceOrder(order Order) error  // Just change it
}

// BAD: Migration code
func MigrateData() {
    if isOldFormat() {
        convertToNew()  // NEVER DO THIS
    }
}

// GOOD: Direct cutover
func LoadData() {
    // Assume new format only
    // Old format fails fast
}
```

