// Use configuration for:
// - Environment-specific values
// - User preferences
// - Tunable parameters
// - Exchange-specific settings
```

#### Big Meanie Specific

```go
// Align with concise naming philosophy
const (
    // BAD: Verbose constant names
    MaximumLeverageAllowed = 10
    MinimumOrderSizeRequired = 0.001
    VolumeSpikeDetectionMultiplier = 2.5

    // GOOD: Concise but clear
    MaxLev = 10
    MinOrd = 0.001
